{"tid":1292653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［長文慎入］今日比兩個老人家搞到喊","createTime":"2019-07-07T11:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T16:13:02.000Z","uid":98813,"like":189,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"df74101efb347021c27326d66c4009826dcd93f1","tid":1292653,"uid":98813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:54:06.000Z","msg":"今日行到柯士甸道，去咗路邊石搏坐低hea。<br />\n<br />\n坐咗無耐，就有兩夫婦，目測70-80歲，行埋嚟我隔離坐低咗。<br />\n<br />\n之後，有幾個記者姐姐離遠眼望望，過多陣仲走埋嚟，問嗰兩位老人家肯唔肯做個訪問。兩位老人家都同意。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">記者問：兩位，見你地都好辛苦咁行到過嚟，究竟系咩原因令你地出嚟遊行呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">婆婆答：反送中囉，同埋想個政府真系回應下市民嘅訴求。我本身都腰痛腳痛，但系我都同我先生出嚟遊行，因為我哋覺得今次有希望，我哋要令政府聽到我哋嘅聲音。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">記者又問：但系好多人話反送中示威好暴力喎，你哋怕唔怕？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">婆婆答：乜嘢暴力姐？整爛幾塊玻璃就話暴力，都無傷害到人。而家死咗4個人呀，林鄭都無回應過，你話邊個暴力呀？仲有呀！繼我話最衰就系tvb，新聞播d唔播d，剪嚟剪去淨系播示威者d衰嘢，根本就係做假新聞，搞到嗰d屋企淨係睇tvb嘅人乜都唔知，一味話d後生仔係暴徒。朝朝飲茶都聽到隔離枱係咁鬧班後生仔，我哋都頂唔順，拿拿林食完就走。<br />\n<br />\n婆婆繼續講：其實我哋今次出嚟，亦都係想支持班後生仔。老實講，我哋當年六四都係企喺學生嗰邊，但係咁多年嚟，政府都唔聽我哋意見，慢慢我地就心灰，真係好灰，以為今次送中肯定過硬啦，多得班後生仔612肯衝肯搏，而家先仲未過到，所以真係好感激班後生仔。佢哋幫我哋做咗咁多嘢，令到我哋有返希望，所以我哋都要出嚟支持佢哋。</span><br />\n<br />\n聽到呢度我已經係咁流眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">跟住記者問：咁婆婆你哋點樣知道反送中嘅嘢呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">婆婆話：我哋有時用手機上網睇直播啦，有時就睇99台，以前就睇有線同埋now，而家就多數用手機睇。</span><br />\n<br />\n跟住記者仲問咗婆婆，除咗今次送中條例之外，政府仲有咩地方令佢哋咁不滿，婆婆就話d超支工程都搞到香港人好激氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">最搞笑係最後婆婆同個記者姐姐講：拿，你哋唔好將我講嘅嘢剪嚟剪去先播出街呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n記者姐姐答：唔會，我哋係明週架！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我真係好想同兩位講，多謝你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"81f69239ea71f7d7ca8a01b8d51a411212a8e943","tid":1292653,"uid":80200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbefa0be91895f3998e1bf8c644cb8267738cf5d","tid":1292653,"uid":98813,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"六月到而家喊咗好多次，但今次真係第一次喺條街度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ba3b4038c4395e5646e149cbf2633432b9d2d7","tid":1292653,"uid":18484,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:59:14.000Z","msg":"明周快d upload<br />\n呢d 訪問要比各大屋企廢老睇  由佢地同齡既人講返說服力大好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aacc6040e3f1b1df9c67de222be81d6da5e4799","tid":1292653,"uid":98813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:00:50.000Z","msg":"香港人加油，我哋嘅努力好多人都睇到，一定會感染到更多人出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"1d9474ce18a396b3b415378e79e99c4158a2676d","tid":1292653,"uid":149487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"c1bfbf20827a5c413a8fe94586b83d40408ed2c6","tid":1292653,"uid":82805,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:02:16.000Z","msg":"系你老母"},{"pid":"b0219efdb109d0f4353c8401ede23e9c051609b1","tid":1292653,"uid":49228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:02:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c58a86a00ce15eaf1cb73ded50d491e9960747b5","tid":1292653,"uid":201464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:04:41.000Z","msg":"入嚟仲以為係廢老鬧到喊"},{"pid":"89ae1b7555c278e67a073cb6f8e1012358b214dc","tid":1292653,"uid":236504,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:05:02.000Z","msg":"婆婆好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知我屋企果兩老幾時先睇得透"},{"pid":"3ea6c3fa23d5db54dd8ac3496b0ffa191002e8b8","tid":1292653,"uid":98813,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c1bfbf20827a5c413a8fe94586b83d40408ed2c6","tid":1292653,"uid":82805,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:02:16.000Z","msg":"系你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:05:07.000Z","msg":"我出完文先見到好多個「系」字，但係我唔係有心架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />較字色嗰陣唔小心㩒錯咗iphone繁轉簡個功能，轉返之後個「系」佢唔幫我轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21b6fc4411bf916409f9616a62ab4ea71a0e91c","tid":1292653,"uid":26353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"記得咁長嘅對答有啲假<br />\n不過照推<br />\n我冇嘢講<br />\n大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85db7ca933b79f42624802b7c5ea486f63b880a2","tid":1292653,"uid":98813,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c21b6fc4411bf916409f9616a62ab4ea71a0e91c","tid":1292653,"uid":26353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"記得咁長嘅對答有啲假<br />\n不過照推<br />\n我冇嘢講<br />\n大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:07:54.000Z","msg":"因為我好專心聽，我都好想了解下會行出嚟嘅老一輩係點睇呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得我係作嘅，我都無辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8801858a6142f058c253720b07cbfb3711d1e2e","tid":1292653,"uid":267240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:07:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9418ad3a43db07a8c5f97d8a29c35582fcecfab","tid":1292653,"uid":98813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89ae1b7555c278e67a073cb6f8e1012358b214dc","tid":1292653,"uid":236504,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:05:02.000Z","msg":"婆婆好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知我屋企果兩老幾時先睇得透"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"只要唔放棄，終有一日佢哋會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f32b81857d1f5c63aee4ca0f666b6c28b7f84b","tid":1292653,"uid":111899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2bc3d5c4c21e8861b48f9bd0dcd41c590b8251","tid":1292653,"uid":275832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:16:53.000Z","msg":"又有兩個好好既記者姐姐"},{"pid":"929326b77393ab7c267419d78b8ac94385ca47c0","tid":1292653,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:19:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cdcf428018cc5fa05f5b83392ad94b7b3fc097bd","tid":1292653,"uid":98813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:22:17.000Z","msg":"可以灰，但唔可以放棄！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd33888004a064e34cc32a2d618b16fa34b09e2","tid":1292653,"uid":146724,"like":1,"dislike":0